## FEEDBACK to VERSION 5
here are some feedbacks:
- All requirement lists are empty, so no actual extraction has occurred.
- Without the full job description text, we cannot populate these fields.
- We need either the job description itself or placeholders indicating where the extracted data should go.

here are the changes:
```json
{
  "job_description": "<<<Please paste the full job description here>>>",
  "job_description_requirements": {
    "skills": [
      "List of required technical and soft skills extracted from the job description"
    ],
    "experience": [
      "List of required years and type of experience (e.g., 5+ years in Java development)"
    ],
    "education": [
      "List of required degrees or certifications (e.g., Bachelor’s in Computer Science)"
    ],
    "responsibilities": [
      "List of core responsibilities (e.g., design and implement REST APIs)"
    ],
    "other": [
      "Any additional requirements (e.g., travel, security clearance, remote/on-site)"
    ]
  }
}
```
